high_descs: Turn around and cross the room and go right and then turn to the left to face the box next to the blue chair.
Pick the box up from the floor.
Turn around and face the end of the white table.
Put the box on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and go toward the wall, turn right at the end of the coffee table, move forward, then turn left to approach the box on the floor.
Pick up the box from the floor.
Turn around and go to the coffee table in front of you.
Put the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a box on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the wall left of the arm chair.
Pick up the box from the floor.
Turn right, move to the coffee table, between the arm chair and coffee table.
Put the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Place a box on the coffee table.
